into planetoids"...

00:02:59.596 --> 00:03:01.556 position:50% align:center
[AO]
Mira. You can do it.

00:03:01.639 --> 00:03:03.099 position:50% align:center
[MIRA] ..."trans-Neptunian
objects are said

00:03:03.183 --> 00:03:06.728 position:50% align:center
