Or maybe aim for another region?

00:09:04.085 --> 00:09:07.005 position:50% align:center
It's 30 minutes
to photograph one region.

00:09:07.088 --> 00:09:09.049 position:50% align:center
And we need time to put
together our presentation

00:09:09.132 --> 00:09:10.508 position:50% align:center
for tomorrow, so...

00:09:10.592 --> 00:09:12.552 position:50% align:center
We only have time for one more.

00:09:12.635 --> 00:09:14.512 position:50% align:center
If you need time to work.

00:09:14.596 --> 00:09:17.307 position:50% align:center
Then I vote that we photograph
the same region again.

00:09:17.390 --> 00:09:20.101 position:50% align:center
We should place our bets
on the highest probability.

00:09:20.185 --> 00:09:21.644 position:50% align:center
I agree!

00:09:21.728 --> 00:09:23.980 position:50% align:center
Okay. Thank you!

00:09:28.193 --> 00:09:30.528 position:50% align:center
Same region, please!

00:09:30.612 --> 00:09:32.197 position:50% align:center
[HANASHIMA]
You've got it.

00:09:40.705 --> 00:09:44.209 position:50% align:center
[MIRA] Okay. Initial processing
of the data is done!

00:09:44.292 --> 00:09:46.211 position:50% align:center
It's the moment of truth!

00:09:46.294 --> 00:09:49.714 position:50% align:center
[MIRA gasps]
Hey, let's push it together!

00:09:49.798 --> 00:09:51.091 position:50% align:center
Of course!

00:09:52.967 --> 00:09:54.803 position:50% align:center
[MAKITA]
Kinda feels like a sports team.

00:09:54.886 --> 00:09:55.887 position:50% align:center
[TOMORI]
What's wrong with that?

00:09:55.970 --> 00:09:57.347 position:50% align:center
Spirits up!

00:09:57.430 --> 00:09:58.932 position:50% align:center
[GIRLS]
One, two...

00:10:03.269 --> 00:10:05.188 position:50% align:center
[MIRA]
It's a known object.

00:10:05.271 --> 00:10:07.482 position:50% align:center
Sorry, that's a shame.

00:10:07.565 --> 00:10:11.236 position:50% align:center
[MIRA] Still, now I know
it's actually within reach.

00:10:11.319 --> 00:10:13.113 position:50% align:center
We can find an asteroid.

00:10:13.196 --> 00:10:15.824 position:50% align:center
It's just a matter of
not giving up till we do!

00:10:15.907 --> 00:10:17.075 position:50% align:center
[AO]
Mm-hmm.

00:10:21.705 --> 00:10:24.290 position:50% align:center
[TOMORI groans]
Presenting our results when we

00:10:24.374 --> 00:10:26.751 position:50% align:center
