understand with pictures!

00:11:12.213 --> 00:11:14.299 position:50% align:center
Aocchi, can I
borrow your camera?

00:11:14.382 --> 00:11:15.550 position:50% align:center
Sure.

00:11:15.633 --> 00:11:16.926 position:50% align:center
Mira, let's write the pages on

00:11:17.010 --> 00:11:19.429 position:50% align:center
